lead_paragraph: Lucas Bjerregaard of Denmark fired a 7-under-par 65 to join Felipe Aguilar of Chile atop the China Open leaderboard after the third round on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Lucas Bjerregaard, Felipe Aguilar Share Lead at China Open
